验证数据
select * from weidashi;
验证是否可以同步
master-1上操作insert into weidashi(name) values('luoshuyu');
以上，主从搭建完毕


3、双向复制master-1操作
stop slave; reset slave;reset slave all;
change master to \
    master_host='172.26.0.136', \
    master_port=3306, \
    master_user='repl', \
    master_password='xiadeng@eebbk.mysql#', \
    master_auto_position=1;
start slave;




4、方案二：双向复制master-1 master-2分别操作
reset master; stop slave; reset slave;reset slave all;

master-2分别操作
change master to \
    master_host='172.26.1.131', \
    master_port=3306, \
    master_user='repl', \
    master_password='xiadeng@eebbk.mysql#', \
    master_auto_position=1;
start slave;

master-1 分别操作
change master to \
    master_host='172.26.0.136', \
    master_port=3306, \
    master_user='repl', \
    master_password='xiadeng@eebbk.mysql#', \
    master_auto_position=1;
start slave;
以上，双向复制搭建完毕！


